stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Designed : Asset Designer\nconfiguration
    Designed --> PendingApproval : Maker submits\nfor review
    PendingApproval --> Approved : Checker approves\n(maker-checker)
    PendingApproval --> Rejected : Checker rejects
    Rejected --> Designed : Revise and\nresubmit
    Approved --> Active : Deploy to\nproduction ledger
    Active --> Suspended : CBE directive\nor limit breach
    Active --> Redeemed : Redemption\nworkflow complete
    Suspended --> Active : Reinstatement\napproved
    Suspended --> Redeemed : Forced redemption
    Redeemed --> Archived : Post-trade\nrecords retained
    Archived --> [*]
